        "subject": "LU-5565 osd-ldiskfs: handle nonexisting objects",
        "message": "LU-5565 osd-ldiskfs: handle nonexisting objects\n\nIn osd_xattr_get() check that the object exists before handling\nXATTR_NAME_VERSION. In osd_xattr_set() add an early -ENOENT return if\nthe supplied object does not exist.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Icb0ccb801aba4ae7799b3021bc6a784f940a13f0\n"
      },
